      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 24
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed in mint condition, and that is a completely honest and accurate representation \u2014 this car is as close to perfect as you will find on the used market. The exterior is genuinely flawless: the paint is deep, glossy, and free of scratches, swirl marks, chips, or blemishes of any kind. The body panels are perfectly aligned, the glass is crystal clear, and all trim pieces are intact and pristine. Step inside and the interior matches the exterior in every way \u2014 the upholstery shows no wear, the carpets are spotless, and every surface looks and feels as though it just left the showroom floor. All electronics, controls, climate systems, and infotainment features function perfectly without exception. Under the hood, the engine is clean, well-maintained, and runs with smooth, confident power. Service records are current and complete. This is a rare opportunity to purchase a used vehicle that genuinely requires nothing \u2014 no repairs, no cosmetic work, no surprises. Buy with complete confidence.",
      "price": 47500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 24
    },
